snippet.title: Blair Witch - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Turn off the lights. Put on the headphones. Prepare for the curse of the Black Hills Forest!

Bloober Team and Lionsgate Games are proud to present the official gameplay from upcoming psychological horror game Blair Witch.

Add to Steam wishlist: http://bit.ly/BW_on_Steam

Official page: https://blairwitchgame.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BlairWitchGame/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/blair_witch_game/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BlairWitchGame

Your darkest fears will awaken on Xbox One and PC on August 30th, 2019.
